snippet.title: Ultimate Simpsons Doom
snippet.description:
Simpsons Doom and Oblige go hand in hand but I'd love to see some maps made specifically with Simpsons Doom in mind. I wonder how good you could actually make a map look using these textures..

http://waltersgameboy.tripod.com/simpdoom/
